QuestData.Title: Fallen But Not Forgotten
QuestData.Description: That was a disaster! Most of our men went down to spears before making it anywhere near the rendezvous.$B$BWe're only going to be able to hold this position for so long before the naga overrun us. We need to get out there to the southwest and save as many of the men as we can find - do anything you can.$B$BThey won't last long. Please hurry!
QuestData.CompletionText: These guys aren't in good shape. We may need to retreat sooner than we'd like.
QuestData.RewardText: Thank you. Truly.$B$BWe need to get these men moving as soon as possible. I'll meet you back at the forward post soon, I'm sure.
